{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2687 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2687 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Compiler Error C2687","pos":[597,617]},{"content":"'type' : exception-declaration cannot be 'void' or denote an incomplete type or pointer or reference to an incomplete type","pos":[618,740]},{"content":"For a type to be part of an exception declaration, it must be defined and not void.","pos":[747,830]},{"content":"The following sample generates C2687:","pos":[837,874]},{"content":"Possible resolution:","pos":[991,1011]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2687 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2687\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2687\"\nms.assetid: 1d24b24a-cd0f-41cc-975c-b08dcfb7f402\ncaps.latest.revision: 8\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2687\n'type' : exception-declaration cannot be 'void' or denote an incomplete type or pointer or reference to an incomplete type  \n  \n For a type to be part of an exception declaration, it must be defined and not void.  \n  \n The following sample generates C2687:  \n  \n```  \n// C2687.cpp  \nclass C;  \n  \nint main() {  \n   try {}  \n   catch (C) {}   // C2687 error  \n}  \n```  \n  \n Possible resolution:  \n  \n```  \n// C2687b.cpp  \n// compile with: /EHsc  \nclass C {};  \n  \nint main() {  \n   try {}  \n   catch (C) {}  \n}  \n```"}